<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>NA UM TAM PIIN RAK PU CH368</title>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa thlua-chuahnak tling tein hmuh awkah na lungthin le, Nunnak he
 na kawl tawn maw? Na Pa biakamnak kha hal law a bia bantukin ra tuah,
 Thluachuah nak lampi chungah.

[C1]
   Na lungthin (Na lungthin cu) cu liam thluahmah in a khahter lai, (a
   khah a liamter lai) Bawipa nih an fial bangin, &quot;Na um vialte rak pu hna,&quot;
   Na lungthin cu (Na lungthin cu) liam thluahmah in a khahter lai. (a khah
   a liamter lai) Thiang-thlarau thawnnak hmual he.

[V2]
 Na um rak pu law Jesuh thi chungah thiang tein tawl tuah, Mi chambau
 hna ra tuah u, Nannih thiannak hmuh awk ah Bawipa thutdan hmai in hngak
 u, Thiang Thlarau a rung tum tiang.

[C2]
   Na lungthin (Na lungthin cu) cu liam thluahmah in a khahter lai, (a
   khah a liamter lai) Bawipa nih an fial bangin, &quot;Na um vialte rak pu hna,&quot;
   Na lungthin cu (Na lungthin cu) liam thluahmah in a khahter lai. (a khah
   a liamter lai) Thiang-thlarau thawnnak hmual he.

[V3]
 Um chung chiti a zor lo bang Bawipa vel zong a dong lo, A dawtnak aa
 thleng bal lo, A thiang thlarau le thawn nak he bia a kan kam bantuk in,
 Um vialte a khahter lai.

[C3]
   Na lungthin (Na lungthin cu) cu liam thluahmah in a khahter lai, (a
   khah a liamter lai) Bawipa nih an fial bangin, &quot;Na um vialte rak pu hna,&quot;
   Na lungthin cu (Na lungthin cu) liam thluahmah in a khahter lai. (a khah
   a liamter lai) Thiang-thlarau thawnnak hmual he.</lyrics>
